<BR>Something nice happened to me last night relating to this topic. I was in Lake Rathetear after a nice jog from FP (I'm a bard) When I do the "/ooc looking for bind in arena". Low and behold, some stranger says follow me, and invites in his group, then runs into the arena. After he binds me, he lets me know that he knew me via another character of his (whom I did remember), and that he enjoyed grouping with me.<P>I claim this as a classic example of how if you try to make friends whenever possible (read: not just twink every newbie you see), its simply amazing how the karma pays for itself later.<P>Hope this helps,<BR>Mithrus Wulfsong<BR>Bard of 27 seasonings<P><P>------------------<BR>(I must taste great, cuz I'm often on the menu)<P>
